text: Silent Wedding () is a 2008 Romanian Luxembourgian French comedy-drama movie. Horațiu Mălăele directed it. Meda Andreea Victor, Alexandru Potocean, Valentin Teodosiu, Nicolae Urs, Tamara Buciuceanu, and Tudorel Filimon acted in the movie. ==Other websites== * Category:2008 comedy-drama movies Category:Romanian comedy movies Category:Romanian drama movies Category:Luxembourgian comedy movies Category:Luxembourgian drama movies Category:French comedy movies Category:French drama movies Category:Movies directed by Horațiu Mălăele
